data.description: Welcome to this cute and cozy home in a prime location that offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and character! This 3-bedroom, 1-bath residence with a 1-car detached garage is a gem waiting for you. There is also a workshop attached to the side of the garage for extra storage and work space.  This property is brimming with potential and is in close proximity to schools, parks, restaurants, shopping centers, and convenient highway access. You'll enjoy the best of both worlds - a peaceful oasis and easy access to the amenities and activities you love.
